text: Robert Galloway and Bradley Klahn were the defending champions but chose not to defend their title. Alex Lawson and Marc Polmans won the title after defeating Hans Hach Verdugo and Dennis Novikov 6–4, 3–6, [10–7] in the final. ==Seeds== ==Draw== ==References== * Main Draw Challenger Banque Nationale de Gatineau - Men's Doubles 2019 Men's Doubles
